3 Andy’s History Andy was born on August 30, 1982 Andy started playing tennis with his older brother John, who was the original tennis playing Roddick After some years of practice and aging, Andy was able to beat John, and he began playing in tournaments Andy started playing in the in US Open Juniors and won He moved up to play in the US Open Men’s Championship to win in 2003 Andy has won many championships since then and is working on more He currently endorses Babolat tennis rackets and shoes, Lacoste sportswear, Lexus automobiles, and Rolex watches
